    "name": "Chonkers",
    "steam_appid": 3244210,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的生活中需要更多的猫，但又担心每月预算不够买那么多猫砂？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别担心！Chonkers 是一款适合猫迷的温馨游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打开门，欢迎最可爱的流浪小猫进入您的房间！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e4beb49ae3d2e52bc8218e96d876097b.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e4beb49ae3d2e52bc8218e96d876097b.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e4beb49ae3d2e52bc8218e96d876097b.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >休息一会儿。放松一下，一边听低保真音乐一边看着他们入睡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e94d30edded734310cbe190d6af900f3.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e94d30edded734310cbe190d6af900f3.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/e94d30edded734310cbe190d6af900f3.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和他们一起玩，让他们更快升级！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/14de4e43bc2fb6102b4134cbb8510cc6.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/14de4e43bc2fb6102b4134cbb8510cc6.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/14de4e43bc2fb6102b4134cbb8510cc6.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让他们胖起来也不用担心健康风险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/53abcaa224cf295db13fa1e0b1e880d8.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/53abcaa224cf295db13fa1e0b1e880d8.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/53abcaa224cf295db13fa1e0b1e880d8.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是数字乐趣。一定要为你的蓬松小朋友寻求专业帮助😸</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你够幸运的话，你也许还能收养最稀有的星际流浪猫。这些来自太空的流浪猫有着迷人的闪亮鬃毛，需要一个新家。给它们一个适当的欢迎 ♥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/5f92f71e2b474eec36b232dde435f1c8.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/5f92f71e2b474eec36b232dde435f1c8.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/5f92f71e2b474eec36b232dde435f1c8.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当您认为它们已经准备好找到新家庭时，就把他们卖掉，换取等重的黄金！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用 100 多个猫品种和 400 多个变种来完善您的收藏书。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/0f3c5190ecb09c5d28db178102b30016.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/0f3c5190ecb09c5d28db178102b30016.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/0f3c5190ecb09c5d28db178102b30016.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您喜欢放松和猫，那么这款游戏就适合您〜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/f072342217588ba50a10c630969a7b92.poster.avif?t=1769610534\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/f072342217588ba50a10c630969a7b92.webm?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244210/extras/f072342217588ba50a10c630969a7b92.mp4?t=1769610534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
